<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jenkins Sandeep Lab</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .projects {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .project {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 30%;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .project h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .project p {
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
        a.button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        a.button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Jenkins Sandeep Lab</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="intro">
        <h2>Welcome to Jenkins Sandeep Lab</h2>
        <p>Your one-stop solution for mastering Jenkins with hands-on labs, projects, and tutorials. Explore our curated resources and elevate your CI/CD skills.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="projects">
        <!-- Example project -->
        <div class="project">
            <h3>Project 1: CI/CD Pipeline</h3>
            <p>Learn how to build and deploy a continuous integration and delivery pipeline using Jenkins. This lab covers everything from basic setup to advanced configuration.</p>
            <a href="#" class="button">Learn More</a>
        </div>
        <div class="project">
            <h3>Project 2: Jenkins Plugins</h3>
            <p>Discover the power of Jenkins plugins. In this tutorial, we explore some of the most popular plugins to enhance your Jenkins experience.</p>
            <a href="#" class="button">Explore Plugins</a>
        </div>
        <div class="project">
            <h3>Project 3: Jenkins Automation</h3>
            <p>Automate repetitive tasks with Jenkins pipelines and scripts. Step into the world of Jenkinsfile and advanced scripting techniques.</p>
            <a href="#" class="button">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Contact us at: sandeep@jenkinslab.com</p>
        <p>Follow us on <a href="#" style="color: #5cb85c;">LinkedIn</a> | <a href="#" style="color: #5cb85c;">GitHub</a> | <a href="#" style="color: #5cb85c;">Twitter</a></p>
